name: corrugated board box production | corrugated board box | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/9509/documentation

This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.;US: production volume = 2.68e+10 kg/year, weight = 0.48031;RER: production volume = 2.80e+10 kg/year, weight = 0.50181;CA-QC: production volume = 9.97e+08 kg/year, weight = 0.01786

The process starts with the feeding of linerboard and corrugated medium to converting facilities.

This activity ends with a mix of folded and unfolded boxes which are then ready for delivery.
category: C:Manufacturing/17:Manufacture of paper and paper products/170:Manufacture of paper and paper products/1702:Manufacture of corrugated paper and paperboard and of containers of paper a

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: This dataset is a weighted average built from the following geographies: US, RER, CA-QC.
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription:
This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.
US: production volume = 2.68e+10 kg/year, weight = 0.48031
RER: production volume = 2.80e+10 kg/year, weight = 0.50181
CA-QC: production volume = 9.97e+08 kg/year, weight = 0.01786
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Inventory data for the RER dataset were collected for the year 2021 ("corrugated board box production, RER" with main reference: FEFCO. 2021. European Database for Corrugated Board Life Cycle Studies. 2021. <https://www.fefco.org/sites/default/files/documents/Fefco_AnnualEvaluation_2021_0.pdf >, accessed March 2023). Data for the CA-QC dataset represent the year 2008 ("corrugated board box production, CA-QC", main data source is data from a manufacturing plant located in the region of Qu√©bec,) and data for the US represent the year 2014 ("corrugated board box production, US", main source NCASI, 2017).
